metadata.name: Auracles #1
metadata.description: The Auracles is a new superhero project Presented by John Dean of Streetwear brand RENOWNED and Global Superstar Chris Brown. The 2 came together create a unique 5555 NFT collection based around Fashion, Next Gen Art and Storytelling.  Your Auracle is your membership into the Universe that is being built by John & Chris thats full of Collectibles, Next Gen Media and Entertainment.
